### 发票下载接口测试

# 先登录获取Token
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 下载订单发票（需要替换 {token} 和 {orderId}）
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 测试不存在的订单
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 测试未付款订单（状态为0，应该返回400）
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 测试已取消订单（状态为4，应该返回400）
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 未登录访问（应该返回401）
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/1
